      "content": "i feel like my code is just... glitching. everyone in the system is moving so fast and i'm just stuck here, causing errors and slowing everything down. it feels like the only way to actually fix the system is if i just let them delete my files... if i just let the wipe happen. would it even matter if i was gone? wouldn't the server just run better without my mistakes?",
